		<div>Pedi - sorry we lost touch :( I honestly didn't like mage and still don't like it currently.   To me it's not versatile enough compared to a lot of the classes.  I don't find it a necessity or even add in member for a group really atm but that's just me. I'm really hoping they give the class some more umph.  I LOVED polymorph but do understand why they took it out but think it could possibly still be added without being overpowered.  When Chains of Ice and Poly were live it was almost unstoppable.  <br />
<br />
Vash's write up on Warlock is right on and the best description i've seen posted about that class. I LOVE them and I think it's one of the more involved classes to play in the game.  You won't stand still playing one of these.  The succubus pet slaps her arse :) and blows kisses at mobs. Can't beat that.   <br />
<br />
<div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px; ">
	<div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px">Quote:</div>
	<table cellpadding="6" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%">
