</div>Pretty fun! If you play in the alliance, you will get a kick out of Duskwood. The cemeteries are overrun with ghouls and skeletons and werewolves. It's like Spooky Hollow. There's one quest that seems harmless at first, but you actually unwittingly end up creating an abomination that slays everything in its path, hellbent on ravaging the town of Darkshire. Town criers will shout out to the area status reports such as the monster overtaking this or that watchpost. You will see miles of corpses of players who want a "go" at taking the abomination down. Tons of fun.<br />
<br />
In the undead lands, all this seems normal and a way of life for them. There are still towns full of human NPCs to slay and the fun thing is that the town turns into werewolves at night.</div>
